parameters: HOLY SHIT! I HAVEN'T SEEN SOMEONE IN LITERALLY
TWO HUNDRED YEARS! HOW THE FUCK ARE YA?
WHAT'S THAT? AN ITEM? YEAH, THERE'S AN ITEM
BEHIND ME, YOU CAN HAVE IT MAN! WEAR IT OR DO
WHATEVER YOU'D LIKE, IT'S YOURS! I'M JUST SO
HAPPY TO HAVE A FRIEND AGAIN!
YEAH MAN, EVERY COUPLE HUNDRED YEARS OR SO
SOMEONE JUST POOFS IN HERE AND OLD GARY HERE
TRIES HIS BEST BUT THEY ALWAYS DIE BECAUSE OF
THE FIRE! SEE ME, I LIKE THE FIRE, I LIKE HOT.
BUT MOST IMPORTANTLY I LIKE FRIENDS. I'M GARY!
YEAH, THERE'S NOT TOO MUCH TO DO HERE, DID YOU
WANT TO PLAY TAG OR SOMETHING?

BEEN IN HERE? I MEAN, I HAVEN'T CHECKED EVERY

A PINCH TOO HOT AND EATING LAVA REALLY MESSES

OUT THERE, I LOOK MEAN BUT I WAS THE PREY, YOU
KNOW WHAT I'M SAYING? OH, IF YOU FIGURE A WAY
OUT, TAKE ME WITH YOU! PLEASE! I'LL FUCKING DO
ANYTHING YOU WANT. ANYTHING! I'LL FIGHT FOR YOU
AND DO YOUR BIDDING! ANYTHING YOU WANT!
SORRY MAN, I'M ALL OUT OF IDEAS. JUST WAIT LIKE
I AM. I MEAN, WE CAN'T BE HERE FOREVER, YOU
